headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid TSN and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Tyson Foods’s shares (currently trading at $51.39) have posted a disappointing 8.4% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 21% gain. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
